30b8"><span class="cl-a235330a">Phone</span></p></td><td class="cl-a2394667"><p class="cl-a23930b8"><span class="cl-a2353314">(512) 447-4141</span></p></td></tr><tr style="overflow-wrap:break-word;"><td class="cl-a2394666"><p class="cl-a23930b8"><span class="cl-a235330a">Website</span></p></td><td class="cl-a2394667"><p class="cl-a23930b8"><a href="http://www.integralcare.org/"><span class="cl-a2353314">http://www.integralcare.org/</span></a></p></td></tr><tr style="overflow-wrap:break-word;"><td class="cl-a2394666"><p class="cl-a23930b8"><span class="cl-a235330a">First Eligibility &amp; Referrals</span></p></td><td class="cl-a2394667"><p class="cl-a23930b8"><span class="cl-a2353314">Male and female ages 18+. Some exclusionary criteria for those with acute medical needs. Referrals received from law enforcement, hospital staff, walk-in crisis services at PES, MCOT, EMCOT and adult behavioral health services.</span></p></td></tr><tr style="overflow-wrap:break-word;"><td class="cl-a2394666"><p class="cl-a23930b8"><span class="cl-a235330a">Cost to Participant</span></p></td><td class="cl-a2394667"><p class="cl-a23930b8"><span class="cl-a2353314">None</span></p></td></tr><tr style="overflow-wrap:break-word;"><td class="cl-a2394666"><p class="cl-a23930b8"><span class="cl-a235330a">Need Category</span></p></td><td class="cl-a2394667"><p class="cl-a23930b8"><span class="cl-a2353314">Behavioral Health Services</span></p></td></tr><tr style="overflow-wrap:break-word;"><td class="cl-a2394666"><p class="cl-a23930b8"><span class="cl-a235330a">Subcategory</span></p></td><td class="cl-a2394667"><p class="cl-a23930b8"><span class="cl-a2353314">Residential Facilities</span></p></td></tr></tbody><tfoot><tr style="overflow-wrap:break-word;"><td  colspan="2"class="cl-a2394668"><p class="cl-a23930b9"><span class="cl-a2353315"></span></p></td></tr><tr style="overflow-wrap:break-word;"><td  colspan="2"class="cl-a2394671"><p class="cl-a23930b9"><span class="cl-a2353315"></span></p></td></t