"><td class="cl-a302b411"><p class="cl-a3029e12"><span class="cl-a2fe21e8">Phone</span></p></td><td class="cl-a302b412"><p class="cl-a3029e12"><span class="cl-a2fe21e9">(512) 447-4141</span></p></td></tr><tr style="overflow-wrap:break-word;"><td class="cl-a302b411"><p class="cl-a3029e12"><span class="cl-a2fe21e8">Website</span></p></td><td class="cl-a302b412"><p class="cl-a3029e12"><a href="http://www.integralcare.org/"><span class="cl-a2fe21e9">http://www.integralcare.org/</span></a></p></td></tr><tr style="overflow-wrap:break-word;"><td class="cl-a302b411"><p class="cl-a3029e12"><span class="cl-a2fe21e8">First Eligibility &amp; Referrals</span></p></td><td class="cl-a302b412"><p class="cl-a3029e12"><span class="cl-a2fe21e9">EMCOT C3s receive direct transfer of calls from 9-1-1 Call Takers when a caller is identified to be in a mental health crisis and there is no immediate public safety or medical emergency identified.</span></p></td></tr><tr style="overflow-wrap:break-word;"><td class="cl-a302b411"><p class="cl-a3029e12"><span class="cl-a2fe21e8">Cost to Participant</span></p></td><td class="cl-a302b412"><p class="cl-a3029e12"><span class="cl-a2fe21e9">Sliding scale</span></p></td></tr><tr style="overflow-wrap:break-word;"><td class="cl-a302b411"><p class="cl-a3029e12"><span class="cl-a2fe21e8">Need Category</span></p></td><td class="cl-a302b412"><p class="cl-a3029e12"><span class="cl-a2fe21e9">Behavioral Health Services</span></p></td></tr><tr style="overflow-wrap:break-word;"><td class="cl-a302b411"><p class="cl-a3029e12"><span class="cl-a2fe21e8">Subcategory</span></p></td><td class="cl-a302b412"><p class="cl-a3029e12"><span class="cl-a2fe21e9">Crisis Intervention Programs</span></p></td></tr></tbody><tfoot><tr style="overflow-wrap:break-word;"><td  colspan="2"class="cl-a302b413"><p class="cl-a3029e13"><span class="cl-a2fe21ea"></span></p></td></tr><tr style="overflow-wrap:break-word;"><td  colspan="2"class="cl-a302b41b"><p class="cl-a3029e13"><span class="cl-