word;"><td class="cl-a310cdc1"><p class="cl-a310baec"><span class="cl-a30ccc84">Phone</span></p></td><td class="cl-a310cdca"><p class="cl-a310baec"><span class="cl-a30ccc8e">(512) 447-4141</span></p></td></tr><tr style="overflow-wrap:break-word;"><td class="cl-a310cdc1"><p class="cl-a310baec"><span class="cl-a30ccc84">Website</span></p></td><td class="cl-a310cdca"><p class="cl-a310baec"><a href="http://www.integralcare.org/"><span class="cl-a30ccc8e">http://www.integralcare.org/</span></a></p></td></tr><tr style="overflow-wrap:break-word;"><td class="cl-a310cdc1"><p class="cl-a310baec"><span class="cl-a30ccc84">First Eligibility &amp; Referrals</span></p></td><td class="cl-a310cdca"><p class="cl-a310baec"><br><span class="cl-a30ccc8e">-  Adults age 18+. </span><br><span class="cl-a30ccc8e">-  Travis County residents. </span><br><span class="cl-a30ccc8e">-  Must meet medical necessity for this level of care and must meet admission medical criteria.</span></p></td></tr><tr style="overflow-wrap:break-word;"><td class="cl-a310cdc1"><p class="cl-a310baec"><span class="cl-a30ccc84">Cost to Participant</span></p></td><td class="cl-a310cdca"><p class="cl-a310baec"><span class="cl-a30ccc8e">Sliding scale</span></p></td></tr><tr style="overflow-wrap:break-word;"><td class="cl-a310cdc1"><p class="cl-a310baec"><span class="cl-a30ccc84">Need Category</span></p></td><td class="cl-a310cdca"><p class="cl-a310baec"><span class="cl-a30ccc8e">Behavioral Health Services</span></p></td></tr><tr style="overflow-wrap:break-word;"><td class="cl-a310cdc1"><p class="cl-a310baec"><span class="cl-a30ccc84">Subcategory</span></p></td><td class="cl-a310cdca"><p class="cl-a310baec"><span class="cl-a30ccc8e">Emergency</span></p></td></tr></tbody><tfoot><tr style="overflow-wrap:break-word;"><td  colspan="2"class="cl-a310cdcb"><p class="cl-a310baed"><span class="cl-a30ccc8f"></span></p></td></tr><tr style="overflow-wrap:break-word;"><td  colspan="2"class="cl-a310cdd5"><p class="cl-a310baed"><span cl