ass="cl-a323efe0"><p class="cl-a323d0aa"><span class="cl-a31d07ac">Phone</span></p></td><td class="cl-a323efe1"><p class="cl-a323d0aa"><span class="cl-a31d07b6">(512) 447-4141</span></p></td></tr><tr style="overflow-wrap:break-word;"><td class="cl-a323efe0"><p class="cl-a323d0aa"><span class="cl-a31d07ac">Website</span></p></td><td class="cl-a323efe1"><p class="cl-a323d0aa"><a href="http://www.integralcare.org/"><span class="cl-a31d07b6">http://www.integralcare.org/</span></a></p></td></tr><tr style="overflow-wrap:break-word;"><td class="cl-a323efe0"><p class="cl-a323d0aa"><span class="cl-a31d07ac">First Eligibility &amp; Referrals</span></p></td><td class="cl-a323efe1"><p class="cl-a323d0aa"><span class="cl-a31d07b6">Referrals are received from community members, schools, and businesses who contact Integral Care’s 24/7 Crisis Helpline (512-472-HELP).</span></p></td></tr><tr style="overflow-wrap:break-word;"><td class="cl-a323efe0"><p class="cl-a323d0aa"><span class="cl-a31d07ac">Cost to Participant</span></p></td><td class="cl-a323efe1"><p class="cl-a323d0aa"><span class="cl-a31d07b6">Sliding scale</span></p></td></tr><tr style="overflow-wrap:break-word;"><td class="cl-a323efe0"><p class="cl-a323d0aa"><span class="cl-a31d07ac">Need Category</span></p></td><td class="cl-a323efe1"><p class="cl-a323d0aa"><span class="cl-a31d07b6">Behavioral Health Services</span></p></td></tr><tr style="overflow-wrap:break-word;"><td class="cl-a323efe0"><p class="cl-a323d0aa"><span class="cl-a31d07ac">Subcategory</span></p></td><td class="cl-a323efe1"><p class="cl-a323d0aa"><span class="cl-a31d07b6">Crisis Intervention Programs</span></p></td></tr></tbody><tfoot><tr style="overflow-wrap:break-word;"><td  colspan="2"class="cl-a323efea"><p class="cl-a323d0b4"><span class="cl-a31d07c0"></span></p></td></tr><tr style="overflow-wrap:break-word;"><td  colspan="2"class="cl-a323eff5"><p class="cl-a323d0b4"><span class="cl-a31d07c0"></span></p></td></tr></tfoot></table></div>
